data.description: Great starter home for young or old! Three bedrooms, two baths, two-car attached garage.Lots of windows, light and bright for that open feeling. Sunroom/gameroom, kitchen with lots of white cabinets(for that clean look), appliances stay. Chain-link fenced back yard with extra concrete for parking. Much like a town home except it has trees and a yard!!! Great buy!
